
	****************************************************************
	            2200/AccuGrid Series NUMONICS digitizing tablet
	****************************************************************

	The NUMONICS drivers will operate with any numonics board  using

the numonics standard interface configuration.  This driver requires a 4

button cursor.   The driver uses a Polling method and reads data from

digitizer in numonics packed binary format (the digitizer must be set for this

format).  The setup is 9600, No Parity, 1 Stop Bit.


